  "id": "RAW_de5f703e",
  "title": "反 AI 的一批人，撑起一家月活过亿的网站",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3NTQ4NjczNw==&mid=2650676601&idx=2&sn=333b87e7d3438004870e9f31f9501df1",
  "date": "2026-01-12 13:34:00",
  "author": "白鲸出海",
  "siteName": "白鲸出海",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 2 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 0 0 auto;border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 4px;border-color: rgb(53, 175, 253);min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;height: auto;padding: 8px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 0px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.46484375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ibJzB4CZdSVXF4K8waZaPrib06kzUT7sic2OQ33ziatiaM7LUkm8Tic9cfoIRCzcDY7whU5QpeNSCs6PRmEaU8My75Tw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"555\" data-cropsely2=\"369\" data-imgfileid=\"503192942\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=35a73b5a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVXF4K8waZaPrib06kzUT7sic2OQ33ziatiaM7LUkm8Tic9cfoIRCzcDY7whU5QpeNSCs6PRmEaU8My75Tw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n     </div>\n     <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">对千禧一代具有强烈吸引力的 Craigslist，会是互联网最后的“净土”吗？</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: right;justify-content: flex-end;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: -1px 0px 10px;transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-26px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;min-width: 5%;max-width: 100%;flex: 0 0 auto;height: auto;padding: 0px 1px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"margin: 4px 0px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(134, 147, 155);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">封面图片由AI生成</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">出品</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 8px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 2 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">｜白鲸出海编辑部</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 AI 和算法全面接管互联网的今天，千禧一代中，仍有不少人选择在 Craigslist 上找工作、谈恋爱，甚至为创意项目选角。他们刻意避开那些被 AI 算法和推荐系统主导的平台，对于 Craigslist，他们给出的评价是：“这里有一种难得的纯粹。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;width:614px !important;box-sizing:border-box !important;height:auto !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">拒绝与时俱进，Craigslist&nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">却收获了一批死忠粉</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">作家兼喜剧演员 Megan Koester 15 年前的第一份工作，来自 Craigslist 上的一则招聘广告，为网络色情内容写评论。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片1.png\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47314814814814815\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"503192943\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=de5e6baa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVXF4K8waZaPrib06kzUT7sic2r3g48kia09fxbiaibfSttiaX389rUM7FN2h9gIDrOiaccQRQomCpicROU85A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px 32px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">图源｜Craigslist</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">几年后，她又靠 Craigslist，找到了居住至今的租金管制公寓。再后来，当她想买一块地皮时，她的方法依旧是刷 Craigslist，最终在莫哈韦沙漠淘到了一块不错的地皮。她在那块地上建了一间小屋。虽然事后才发现自己的小屋是违规建筑 （ 因为手续没办全 ），但屋内的所有陈设，几乎都来自 Craigslist 的“免费专区”，就连地板是都从一家影视制作公司淘来的二手复合地板。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“我生活的方方面面，都被 Craigslist 渗透了。”42 岁的 Koester 分享道。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">她的 Instagram 账号里，有相当一部分内容是她在 Craigslist 免费区截下来的“惊悚图片合集”。与媒体对话当天，她穿的那件羊绒衫也没花一分钱。全凭 Koester 胆子大，在 Craigslist 回了个连图都没有的帖子，就免费得到了，“我跟这网站算是锁死了。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Koester 只是众多 Craigslist 拥趸中的一员。很多用户正处在三四十岁的年纪，他们不仅仍在使用这个看起来“老掉牙”的分类信息网站，甚至把它当作日常生活中不可或缺的一部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Craigslist&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">依然允许用户匿名，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不一定要发生金钱交易，谈情说爱、为角色选演员，这些需求下也</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">能和陌生人产生真实联结</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">和 DePop、Etsy、Facebook Marketplace 这些“现代化”的平台不同，Craigslist 不靠算法追踪用户行为，也不“猜你喜欢”；既没有公开主页、评分系统，也没有点赞、转发这些“社交货币”。 Craigslist 几乎抑制了所有刷存在感和追逐流量的行为，与 TikTok、Instagram 和 X 等平台背道而驰，像是</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">早期互联网的乌托邦缩影。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" alt=\"图片2.png\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6083333333333333\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-imgfileid=\"503192944\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=85f38171&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVXF4K8waZaPrib06kzUT7sic2bAVKLHfOZM3oej2xaHiburWMRhhA9X2AGjmfDZs9RWCibKuDVTATwgVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">有人曾在 Craigslis 上交换了 4.5 万</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px;line-height: 1em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">封电子“情书”后结婚｜图源 WIRED</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“真正的怪咖都会出现在 Craigslist 上。”Koester 说，“但它有一种纯粹感”。当然，如今的 Craigslist 已经比过去规范许多。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2018 年，美国国会通过了一项针对网络交易的法案后，Craigslist 关闭了“随意约会”板块，并下线了整个交友栏目。但被保留的“错过邂逅”（Missed Connections）区仍然活跃。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:32px 8px 8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 5 []\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:614px !important;margin-top:0px;height:auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">无算法、不猜你喜欢，</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">“落后”即是魅力点</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">宾夕法尼亚大学传播学副教授 Jessa Lingel 曾</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">把 Craigslist 称为“未中产化的互联网”。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">依照这个说法，近几年互联网的“中产化”可谓神速，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">而AI 技术的贡献则功不可没</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。即便是 Wikipedia 和 Reddit 这样页面朴素、强调社区氛围的网站，也已经陆续加入了自家的 AI 工具。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">15 年前，Wired 给 Craigslist 的评价是“发育不全”、“难以预测”；但对其“死忠粉”来说</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">，这恰恰是它的魅力所在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“Craigslist 正迎来复兴”，副业为演员兼喜剧人的 Kat Toledo 这样认为。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">她经常通过 Craigslist 为自己在洛杉矶的脱口秀节目《Besitos》招募搭档。“</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">当一个网站结构足够简单，真正服务社区，又几乎不向用户索取什么，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">这样的网站反而更容易活下来。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片3.png\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503192945\" data-ratio=\"0.6650426309378806\" data-w=\"821\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=469d7aec&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVXF4K8waZaPrib06kzUT7sic2YoU3HGXb12ZI5VXtz3niaftgIPD9Wsfw82lWt48vQ1jmALYhuichqTyQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">图源｜WIRED</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">Toledo 从 2000 年代开始使用 Craigslist，是网站最忠实的用户之一。</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">她用 Craigslist 找过恋爱对象、房子，甚至找到了现在的正职，在一位法医心理学家手下做助理。她已经全职干了快两年，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">打破了 Craigslist 只提供“零工”机会的刻板印象。</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">Craigslis 长期背负着负面名声，总让人联想到骗局，甚至在极端案例中与谋杀联系在一起。Toledo 偶尔会跟雇主开玩笑：“如果我哪天干得不好，就想想你可是在 Craigslist 上招到我的。”</span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\">但在她看来，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Craigslist 最迷人的地方正是这种“随机性”</span>，能让你与平时根本不会产生交集的人产生联系。Toledo 发布的付费搭档招募广告，吸引来的大多是“那种没啥可输、但啥都可能赢一把的人”。有人是基督徒，要在舞台上重现自己的信仰觉醒；有人是诗人，非要给 Toledo 化妆；还有个商业演员，通话时突然开哭，但最终也没登台。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:32px 8px 8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"5 5 []\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.07871720116618076\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1029\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible !important;letter-spacing:0.544px;vertical-align:bottom;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;width:614px !important;margin-top:0px;height:auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"503183761\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=156887aa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVVZ7JnPtEEqnkicw1JmIUibze4kI4o76tr2zVE3LC8g6wTX3sBXRJLOJP3ick53GT05KzcjvVROmLoJA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%26wx_co%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic\"></span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">没什么商业化、也“不卖身”，</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;word-spacing:0px;outline:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:8px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:none;widows:2;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;font-size: 16px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;color: rgb(53, 175, 253);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">但能长期盈利？</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Craigslist 的活跃用户数和点击量很难统计，这家私人控股的公司从不公开用户数据，也不回复媒体的对谈请求。但据 Similarweb 统计，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Craigslist 月活用户超 1.05 亿</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">，在美国网站中位列第 40，对于不怎么打广告、又不营销的公司来说，这是一个相当可以的成绩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">尽管行业分析机构估计其近 6年收入大幅下滑，但 Craigslist&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">依然利润惊人</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。公司主要通过对招聘信息、某些商品广告和部分城市的房源信息收取少量费用盈利。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“Craigslist 当然不完美，但它至少证明了一件事：你完全</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">可以在不榨取用户数据的前提下，在互联网上赚钱。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Lingel 表示自己也是 Craigslist 的长期用户。正是因为这个网站，她开始思考：“为什么所有 Web 2.0 公司都坚称，只有靠用户数据才能成功、才能盈利？世界上一定存在别的路子。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 32px 16px 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片4.png\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503192946\" data-ratio=\"0.30277777777777776\" data-w=\"1080\" data-type=\"png\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e4453f81&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FibJzB4CZdSVXF4K8waZaPrib06kzUT7sic21QicSEpI8iaiaj6f7r5tANnicgIr4No9xqePh97SaxeGXx1iapG23yYjEicg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin: 0px 8px 32px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">图源｜press.princeton.edu</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Lingel 在书中追溯了&nbsp;</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Craigslist 的历史</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1995 年，它只是工程师 Craig Newmark 的一个实验产品，一份面向旧金山湾区几百人的邮件列表，用来分享活动信息、科技新闻和招聘信息。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">90 年代末，这个实验产品逐渐变成了一家正式公司，拥有了办公室、域名和几名员工。很有 Craigslist 风格的一件事是，Newmark 最初在网站上发广告，只想找一名程序员，结果招来了后来的网站 CEO Jim Buckmaster。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这两人一直努力让 Craigslist 远离资本的侵蚀。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2004 年，eBay 从一名前员工手中买下 Craigslist 的少数股份后，Newmark 和 Buckmaster 察觉到潜在的收购风险，与这家科技巨头打了将近十年的官司。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">2015 年，Craigslist 回购股份，重新完全掌控公司。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">“他们在坚持 90 年代早期互联网价值观这件事上，步调完全一致。”Lingel 说。正是 Newmark 和 Buckmaster，让 Craigslist 始终保持着</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">简洁、隐私优先、人人可用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">的设计与精神。“只要他们还是大股东，这一点就不会变。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在 Koester 看来，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">这种“拒绝卖身”的态度，正是她追随 Craigslist 的原因</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。“不只是用户群体很纯粹，管理层本身也很纯粹，他们几乎是不可腐蚀的。”她说，“我会一直刷 Craigslist，直到我死。”她顿了顿，打了个寒颤又开口：“或者，等 Craig 先死吧。”</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">本篇编译自 Is Craigslist the Last Real Place on the Internet? - WIRED</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 32px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);\">原文链接：<a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/is-craigslist-the-last-real-place-on-the-internet/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.com/story/is-craigslist-the-last-real-place-on-the-internet/</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "报告深入分析了 Craigslist 在 AI 时代反其道而行，通过坚持匿名、不算法推荐的简洁模式，反而获得了月活过亿的商业成功，证明了互联网产品差异化竞争的可能性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "报告深入分析了 Craigslist 在 AI 时代反其道而行，通过坚持匿名、不算法推荐的简洁模式，反而获得了月活过亿的商业成功，证明了互联网产品差异化竞争的可能性。",
  "summary": "本文深度剖析了分类信息网站 Craigslist 在 AI 和算法主导的现代互联网中，如何凭借其“反科技”的简洁风格和匿名机制，吸引并留住了一批忠实用户，实现月活过亿的商业成功。文章通过用户案例和专家访谈，阐释了 Craigslist 坚持不依赖算法推荐、不收集用户数据、保持开放和去中心化的运营模式，以及公司创始人抵抗资本侵蚀的坚持，证明了在数字时代，不“中产化”的互联网产品也能盈利，并为用户提供一种“纯粹”的连接体验。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Craigslist 通过反主流的简洁设计和匿名机制，在现代互联网中找到独特的用户价值。",
      "explanation": "在 AI 和算法主导的时代，Craigslist 坚持不追踪用户行为、不进行算法推荐、没有社交压力，反而吸引了寻求“纯粹”连接和互动体验的用户群体。"
    },
    {
      "point": "用户对 Craigslist 的高忠诚度源于其提供的独特“随机性”和去中心化社区感。",
      "explanation": "Craigslist 允许用户匿名发布和寻找各类信息，促成了用户之间意想不到的真实连接，而非算法筛选后的同质化体验，培养了一批高度依赖其服务的忠实拥趸。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Craigslist 证明了不依赖用户数据和算法盈利的新型商业模式的可行性。",
      "explanation": "公司通过对招聘、房源等特定信息收取费用，在不“榨取”用户数据的前提下实现了长期盈利，挑战了 Web 2.0 时代“数据为王”的主流商业逻辑。"
    },
    {
      "point": "创始人坚守早期互联网价值观是 Craigslist 长期成功的关键。",
      "explanation": "创始人 Craig Newmark 和 Jim Buckmaster 始终致力于让网站保持简洁、隐私优先和人人可用，并通过回购股份抵抗资本的侵蚀，确保了其独特的产品理念不被商业利益所稀释。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "这里有一种难得的纯粹。",
    "我生活的方方面面，都被 Craigslist 渗透了。",
    "真正的怪咖都会出现在 Craigslist 上。",
    "当一个网站结构足够简单，真正服务社区，又几乎不向用户索取什么，这样的网站反而更容易活下来。",
    "你完全可以在不榨取用户数据的前提下，在互联网上赚钱。"
  ],
  "tags": [
    "商业模式",
